{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"59516464-56e6-45b6-b1c8-7be9e86d2f2a","content":"The `.testsettings` format is **legacy** and ignored by modern MSTest (v3+). You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Your file configures three things:\n\n1. **Test timeout** (30 s)\n2. **Code coverage** data collector\n3. **Assembly resolution** (no longer needed — handled automatically)\n\nHere's the equivalent `.runsettings`:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_012wefFJxekKQ42ni7nxzaxR","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01L1M8pbU3qAQse6kzdjKkLh","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-3af2d269c107426fa9af705e003355df/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <!-- Replaces <Property name=\"TestTimeout\" value=\"30000\" /> -->\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <!-- Replaces the legacy CodeCoverage DataCollector -->\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.SingleFileCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-3af2d269c107426fa9af705e003355df/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"172b753f-cdb5-4e83-a329-cc54612303ac","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file that configures:\n1. Test timeout of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n2. Code coverage data collector\n3. Assembly resolution with `useLoadContext`\n\nThe `.testsettings` format is legacy and not supported by the modern MSTest/VSTest platform. They need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file.\